WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.372 --> 00:00:09.575
LITTLE DONNY HAS ALWAYS
BEEN SO SPECIAL TO US.

00:00:09.608 --> 00:00:14.214
HE'S GOT AN ENTHUSIASM
YOU CAN'T FIND ANYWHERE ELSE.

00:00:15.614 --> 00:00:17.583
YOU THINK YOU'VE
GOT PROBLEMS,

00:00:17.616 --> 00:00:20.820
AND THEN YOU SEE DONNY
AND WHAT HE HAS TO DEAL WITH,

00:00:20.853 --> 00:00:24.357
AND THE WAY HE'S ALWAYS
FULL OF JOY AND HAPPINESS,

00:00:24.390 --> 00:00:26.092
AND HE'S SO OPEN
TO PEOPLE.

00:00:26.125 --> 00:00:27.193
IT PUTS THINGS
IN PERSPECTIVE.

00:00:28.194 --> 00:00:30.229
OH, DONNY'S GREAT.

00:00:30.262 --> 00:00:32.131
VERY BRIGHT.

00:00:32.164 --> 00:00:35.668
SOMETIMES HE GETS SAD WHEN HE
SEES THE KIDS IN THE PLAYGROUND

00:00:35.701 --> 00:00:37.570
AND HE'S
STUCK IN INSIDE.

00:00:37.603 --> 00:00:40.673
BUT GENERALLY,
HE'S A REALLY HAPPY KID.

00:00:42.775 --> 00:00:47.013
DONNY HAS MORE HEART THAN
MOST ATHLETES TWICE HIS SIZE.

00:00:50.416 --> 00:00:52.418
I JUST WANT DONNY
TO BE HAPPY,

00:00:52.451 --> 00:00:54.420
TO FIND SOMEBODY
WHO'LL LOVE HIM.

00:00:54.453 --> 00:00:57.690
TO BE ABLE TO FIT IN
WITH EVERYBODY ELSE.

00:00:57.723 --> 00:01:01.327
WHAT I WANT FOR DONNY IS
FREEDOM TO BE A NORMAL KID.

00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:04.363
I'LL DO ANYTHING TO
HELP HIM GET THROUGH LIFE

00:01:04.396 --> 00:01:06.833
WITHOUT THE DISABILITY
INFRINGING ON

00:01:06.866 --> 00:01:08.334
HIS ABILITY
TO ENJOY LIFE.

00:01:12.238 --> 00:01:14.307
THIS HOLIDAY SEASON,

00:01:14.340 --> 00:01:17.243
THE LITTLE DONNY FOUNDATION
IS ASKING FOR YOUR SUPPORT.

00:01:17.276 --> 00:01:20.947
WITH YOUR HELP, WE HOPE TO CURE
"LITTLE DONNY DISEASE"

00:01:20.980 --> 00:01:25.151
BEFORE ANOTHER CHILD LIKE DONNY
BECOMES AFFLICTED WITH:

00:01:25.184 --> 00:01:27.554
A PENIS THE SIZE
OF A HORSE'S.

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:36.829
DONNY IS THE FIRST
DOCUMENTED CASE

00:01:36.862 --> 00:01:40.266
OF WHAT WE HAVE LABELED,
MAGNAMOUS OBLIVIO PHALLUSITIS,

00:01:40.299 --> 00:01:41.968
IN LAYMAN'S TERMS,

00:01:42.001 --> 00:01:45.338
HAVING AN ENORMOUS PENIS
WHICH YOU ARE UNAWARE OF.

00:01:49.008 --> 00:01:52.912
I WANT TO SHOW YOU SOME OF THE
SAFETY DEVICES I'VE DEVELOPED

00:01:52.945 --> 00:01:55.848
TO HELP DONNY LEAD
A MORE NORMAL LIFE.

00:01:55.881 --> 00:01:58.684
I HAVE TO SAY, I DON'T
LIKE THESE DEVICES.

00:01:58.717 --> 00:02:01.654
I THINK THEY CALL ATTENTION
TO HIS DISEASE.

00:02:01.687 --> 00:02:03.523
THEY MAKE HIM
FEEL DIFFERENT.

00:02:03.556 --> 00:02:06.626
AND, HIS PENIS IS
REALLY NOT THAT BIG.

00:02:06.659 --> 00:02:10.329
HIS PENIS ACCOUNTS FOR OVER
13% OF HIS TOTAL BODY WEIGHT.

00:02:10.362 --> 00:02:11.898
WE DON'T NEED TO
TALK ABOUT THIS--

00:02:11.931 --> 00:02:14.934
MOMMY, I GOT A
CHOCOLATE MILK MUSTACHE !

00:02:14.967 --> 00:02:19.839
WE'RE GONNA SHOW THESE GUYS
SOME DEVICES I'VE DEVELOPED.

00:02:19.872 --> 00:02:21.140
NO !

00:02:21.173 --> 00:02:22.608
COME ON, DONNY.

00:02:22.641 --> 00:02:24.410
YES.

00:02:24.443 --> 00:02:27.914
NOT ALL THE DEVICES HAVE BEEN
AS SUCCESSFUL AS I HOPED.

00:02:27.947 --> 00:02:29.982
THIS IS CALLED
A "PENIS STRAP",

00:02:30.015 --> 00:02:33.386
AND THE PROBLEM IS THAT
IT CAUSED SOME CHAFING--

00:02:33.419 --> 00:02:35.521
NO !

00:02:35.554 --> 00:02:39.926
TO HOLD THE PENIS DOWN,
YOU HAVE TO CINCH IT TIGHT.

00:02:39.959 --> 00:02:41.994
OW !

00:02:42.027 --> 00:02:44.530
IT'S ALMOST OVER,
SWEETIE.

00:02:44.563 --> 00:02:46.266
OKAY, OKAY.

00:02:48.500 --> 00:02:50.136
I GOTTA GET HIM.

00:02:51.570 --> 00:02:53.272
UMM...

00:02:53.305 --> 00:02:59.145
DONNY REALLY LIKES
CHOCOLATE MILK.

00:02:59.178 --> 00:03:01.113
I LOVE
LITTLE DONNY,

00:03:01.146 --> 00:03:04.784
'CAUSE HE ALWAYS COMES BY
AND VISITS US SICK KIDS.

00:03:04.817 --> 00:03:07.920
SOMETIMES,
I CAN'T BREATHE,

00:03:07.953 --> 00:03:10.556
OR KEEP ANY
FOOD DOWN.

00:03:10.589 --> 00:03:12.959
BUT WHEN LITTLE DONNY
COMES BY

00:03:12.992 --> 00:03:16.462
HE DANCES,
AND I JUST LAUGH--

00:03:16.495 --> 00:03:19.299
( coughing )

00:03:22.301 --> 00:03:24.704
IF I DO NOT DIE,

00:03:24.737 --> 00:03:28.007
I WANT LITTLE DONNY
AT MY BIRTHDAY PARTY,

00:03:28.040 --> 00:03:30.343
AND HIS BIG
PENIS TOO.

00:03:30.376 --> 00:03:32.578
WE COULD
LAUGH A LOT,

00:03:32.611 --> 00:03:35.215
AND THEN WE COULD
HAVE CAKE.

00:03:36.949 --> 00:03:39.152
( coughing )

00:03:41.387 --> 00:03:44.190
I GUESS THIS DONNY'S
IN FOR SOME TESTS.

00:03:44.223 --> 00:03:46.359
THESE GET-A-WISH KIDS
ARE ALL THE SAME.

00:03:46.392 --> 00:03:48.794
THE PROBLEM IS THEY
FEEL SORRY FOR THEMSELVES.

00:03:48.827 --> 00:03:51.197
SO I JUST TRY TO SHAKE
THEM UP A LITTLE.

00:03:51.230 --> 00:03:54.900
I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHAT'S
THE MATTER WITH THIS KID.

00:03:54.933 --> 00:03:57.103
HO HO HO HO !

00:03:57.136 --> 00:03:58.904
HELLO, HELLO,
HELLO !

00:03:58.937 --> 00:04:02.175
IS SOMEONE FEELING
SORRY FOR THEMSELVES ?

00:04:06.979 --> 00:04:09.482
YOU'RE NOT
THE TITTE BROTHERS.

00:04:09.515 --> 00:04:11.817
THE TITTE BROTHERS
COULDN'T MAKE IT.

00:04:11.850 --> 00:04:14.553
I'M THE WORLD'S PREMIER
OUTER-FRINGE ATHLETE

00:04:14.586 --> 00:04:17.723
AND A PUSSY'S
WORSE NIGHTMARE.

00:04:17.756 --> 00:04:19.959
ARE YOU
A PUSSY DONNY ?

00:04:19.992 --> 00:04:22.261
WHAT'S SO BAD
THAT YOU HAVE TO--

00:04:22.294 --> 00:04:24.297
WHAT THE HELL
IS THAT ?

00:04:24.330 --> 00:04:27.767
( man )
HE HAS ENORMOUS PENIS,
BUT HE'S UNAWARE OF IT.

00:04:27.800 --> 00:04:30.770
WELL, WE'RE GONNA TURN
A NEGATIVE INTO A POSITIVE.

00:04:30.803 --> 00:04:32.705
GET UP, DONNY !

00:04:34.707 --> 00:04:36.609
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU
GOT BETWEEN YOUR LEGS ?

00:04:36.642 --> 00:04:39.245
YOU GOT A MAGNIFICENT
GOD-GIVEN WEAPON.

00:04:39.278 --> 00:04:40.846
NOW SWING YOUR HIPS,
DONNY.

00:04:40.879 --> 00:04:43.549
PUMP 'EM, PUMP 'EM !

00:04:44.917 --> 00:04:47.987
THAT'S A TWO-FOOT
DEFLECTIVE BARRIER !

00:04:49.288 --> 00:04:50.556
COME ON, COME ON !

00:04:50.589 --> 00:04:51.590
WHAT ?

00:04:51.623 --> 00:04:52.958
ATTACK HIM !

00:04:52.991 --> 00:04:54.661
I AIN'T GOING NEAR
THAT THING.

00:04:57.529 --> 00:05:00.032
COME ON, DONNY,
HARDER !

00:05:00.065 --> 00:05:01.034
GET DOWN !

00:05:04.203 --> 00:05:10.343
THERE YOU GO,
YOU DID THAT, DONNY !

00:05:10.376 --> 00:05:12.578
AND WHEN WE WERE
DOING OUR FINALE,

00:05:12.611 --> 00:05:16.015
SOME OF THE DANCERS NOTICED
MOVEMENT IN THE AUDITORIUM,

00:05:16.048 --> 00:05:17.717
AND BEFORE
WE KNEW IT,

00:05:17.750 --> 00:05:21.287
THIS YOUNG MAN DONNY,
HAD ROSE OUT OF HIS SEAT,

00:05:21.320 --> 00:05:23.456
AND WAS IN
THE AISLES DANCING,

00:05:23.489 --> 00:05:28.094
AND CREATING SUCH AN INCREDIBLE
VOCABULARY OF MOVEMENT,

00:05:28.127 --> 00:05:31.697
IT WAS MUCH MORE INSPIRING
THAN THE WORK ONSTAGE.

00:05:31.730 --> 00:05:34.533
FORTUNATELY, HE CAME
BACKSTAGE AFTER THE SHOW.

00:05:34.566 --> 00:05:37.570
WE ASKED HIM
TO COME JOIN US.

00:05:37.603 --> 00:05:40.573
WE'RE IN REHEARSAL
FOR A NEW PIECE

00:05:40.606 --> 00:05:44.977
WHICH IS INSPIRED BY
DONNY'S MOVEMENT AND FREEDOM,

00:05:45.010 --> 00:05:46.679
IT'S ASTONISHING.

00:05:50.482 --> 00:05:52.518
WE DON'T KNOW MUCH
ABOUT THE DISEASE,

00:05:52.551 --> 00:05:56.255
BUT IT HAS MOSTLY
TO DO WITH GENETICS,

00:05:56.288 --> 00:05:59.091
AS OPPOSED TO SOMETHING
THAT MAY HAVE GONE WRONG

00:05:59.124 --> 00:06:00.960
IN A DELIVERY ROOM.

00:06:00.993 --> 00:06:04.530
THE LITTLE DONNY FOUNDATION
WAS FORMED IN 1992,

00:06:04.563 --> 00:06:07.566
BY AN INTERNATIONAL TEAM OF
DOCTORS AND SCIENTISTS,

00:06:07.599 --> 00:06:10.870
WHO SHARED A PASSION
FOR LITTLE DONNY'S PENIS.

00:06:10.903 --> 00:06:14.407
SINCE THEN, MANY DISCOVERIES
HAVE BEEN MADE,

00:06:14.440 --> 00:06:17.710
BUT UNFORTUNATELY,
A CURE HAS YET TO BE FOUND.

00:06:22.347 --> 00:06:26.018
WITH THE ENZYMES WE PULLED
OUT OF LITTLE DONNY'S PENIS,

00:06:26.051 --> 00:06:28.454
WE WERE ABLE TO DEVELOP
A ROCKET FUEL

00:06:28.487 --> 00:06:32.125
WITH 38% INCREASED
EFFICIENCY.

